The Wormhole Studio's   "Urban Houses"

These houses are from the map "CS_Motel_TWS" (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/106757)

If you use these houses in a map, then please put "The Wormhole Studios" in the credits!

-------
INSTALL
-------

1. Put the "TWS_House2.vmf" and the "TWS_House1.vmf" here:
   C:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\ (steam account) \sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefabs

2. Put the folder named "TWS_Prefab" here:
   C:\Program\Steam\SteamApps\ (steam account) \counter-strike source\cstrike\materials

-------
CREDITS
-------

Custom Texture - The Wormhole Studios

Prefab - The Wormhole Studios

-----------

Visit:

http://steamcommunity.com/groups/thewormholestudios

---------

(EDIT)  IMPORTANT - These houses are for display only; you can't go inside but they look really great to fill out a map with!
